flowchart TD
    A[Start: Open IntelliSched] --> B[Load CSV Data]
    B --> C[Clean & Normalize Data]
    C --> D[Initialize Schedule Population]
    D --> E[Evaluate Fitness (Hard/Soft Constraints)]
    E --> F{Conflicts Acceptable?}
    F -- No --> G[Evolve (Selection, Crossover, Mutation)]
    G --> E
    F -- Yes --> H[Finalize Best Schedule]
    H --> I[Validate & Generate Report]
    I --> J[Render Views (Day/Section/Performance)]
    J --> K[End: Export/Present Results]
